621
00:50:57,210 --> 00:50:59,900
Ale ne tenhle dům a motely.

622
00:51:01,060 --> 00:51:05,550
Protože tu žije noční tvor Jo Dong Min

623
00:51:05,550 --> 00:51:08,500
